h2. Other distributions

For all distributions that don't have specific packages yet, we offer a universal binary.
You need to install the following dependencies, either from your package manager or by following the links below:

* "Qt >= 4.3.0":http://trolltech.com/developer/downloads/qt/x11
* "Python >= 2.4":http://www.python.org/download/
* "SIP >= 4.7":http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/sip/download.php
* "PyQt4 >= 4.3":http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/pyqt/download.php

